In the maximal base, the heat rises in CR chamber number 4. As it 
crawls to 49,6 celsius to 49,7 and then to 49,8, the robot inside 
starts to move. An arm, then a foot. Then the chest. And the head.

The eyes. They both open, revealing a ravenous and murderous fury.

The mouth. A feral growl echoes through the whole base.

The claws. Striking hard and fast, they bump and destroy the door.

The legs. The beast jumps onto CR chamber number 2 and perches itself 
there.

His breath is quick, his teeth are bared, his fur is standing straight 
on his body. He looks around, not distracted by the alarm caused by 
his exit.

Blackfang lives again...
